418
00:22:00,160 --> 00:22:02,040
I like the kind of girl like you.
Very stable.

419
00:22:03,760 --> 00:22:06,230
You are different from other girls
who are fond of muddling along.

420
00:22:07,520 --> 00:22:10,710
