421
00:22:13,310 --> 00:22:15,560
A little.

422
00:22:15,800 --> 00:22:18,280
Miss Xing, I am very satisfied with you.

423
00:22:19,400 --> 00:22:20,710
When you are available,

424
00:22:20,710 --> 00:22:21,920
